data.description: Nestled within the idyllic Belle Savanne Subdivision, this captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a true gem, boasting an impressive 1710 square feet of luxurious living space. With its charming curb appeal, modern amenities, and thoughtful design, this residence offers an unparalleled living experience. Step inside to discover a harmonious blend of elegance and functionality. The heart of the home welcomes you with an open-concept layout, seamlessly connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Gleaming granite countertops adorn the kitchen, perfectly complementing the warm hues of the birchwood cabinets. A convenient pantry provides ample storage, making culinary endeavors a delight. Sunlight dances through custom blinds, casting a radiant glow upon the entire house. The spacious living area is bathed in natural light, creating an inviting ambiance for relaxation and gatherings. Unwind in the grandeur of the master suite, featuring a sumptuous en-suite bathroom complete with double vanities, ensuring a pampering experience each day. The allure of the master is further enhanced by a generous walk-in closet, offering an abundance of space for your wardrobe and personal treasures. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms provide comfort and versatility, catering to your unique needs. An extra bathroom exudes modern elegance, enhancing both style and convenience. Stepping outdoors, the front of the house gives an unimpeded view of the glimmering pond. Savor the tranquility of your private oasis. The lush .15-acre lot provides ample space for outdoor recreation. This property truly encompasses the essence of modern comfort and style, where every detail has been meticulously curated to elevate your everyday living experience.
